Metalworking Table
-allows for the creation of many "Metal" parts

Crafting Recipe

OOO   Obsidian       =O     Furnace  =F
CWC  CobbleStone =C
CFC   Workbench   =W

Metalworking Table
Recipes
-9 "metal" leaves -> 1 "metal" sheet
-9 "metal" sheets -> 1 "metal" ingot
-1 "metal" nugget -> 9 "metal" leaves

-3 "metal" sheets -> 1 "metal" rod
-3 "metal" rods     -> 3 "metal" tubes
 
